Intro

This document summarizes some of the exploratory data analysis of the Prudhoe Bay nearshore fisheries data by Justin Priest for The Data Wrangling Seminar, Fish 692. https://github.com/justinpriest/Fish692-DataWranglingSeminar

Catch Histograms for select species (Response Variables)

Note that most catches are very right skewed

Environmental Histograms (explanatory variables)

Note that salinity has dropped at the eastern sites (230&214) and increased at the western sites (220&218)

Note that temperature has significantly increased at all sites!
